Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.40,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}翻譯：無、AppleJack  校對：Radium  後期：九陽飛羽  繁化：小新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 看來我也許確實錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道定量的蛋糕買不光會怎樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那可真是讓人傷心透了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別 甜品 專櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我改成了下單才做的制度了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在這種鄉下 需求也還是有的呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在賣得不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫃檯 電話還是互聯網們都可以訂購
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互網網…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互聯網…網…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互聯…互聯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互聯網啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是互聊網啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你剛剛把什麽藏起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我在寫目記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 比起這個你聽我説
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也搞互聯網網購!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你要買漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系介樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗點心和店裡的玩具之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過網絡來賣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實現在那樣做會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以為此我們要先做出我們店的主頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先嘗試著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了一個看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一是互聯網強人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hypertext Markup Language什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是義務教育級別的水平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是那個有名的HTML…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼這個樣子的話太樸素了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麽東西跟著跟隨著鼠標的移動在閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個超級懷念的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Java Script哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是那個有名的Java Script
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 電腦什麼都能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是文明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先賣些什麽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣傳要點是什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣傳…宣傳要點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我們賣粗點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣傳過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字咻地飄過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽老長的文字咻地不停飄過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個再這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很…很閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把在賣粗點心的亂強調一氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是粗點心店嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿田粗點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽感覺變得這麽有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這張照片上傳 放到主頁上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是店長（暫定）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛有打上碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把這個這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多個我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 難得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把我放上去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打碼太麻煩了 用手代替
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 寫上粗點心能送貨上門還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後還要寫什麽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有粗點心店的懷舊之情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個部份强調一下的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 懷舊感對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「鹿田」員工 一醬（ 20歲 ）給你最淳樸的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是在做粗點心店的宣傳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 我們也賣玩員之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,☆也有玩具…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是… 配送粗點心這也輸進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得有點太過火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就是乘興做過頭的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是於是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 訂貨估計會在中午前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長你訂了什麼貨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你説交給你來訂的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道説你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然今天就會送到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘記啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 現在網購的話今天還送得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個吧 超級彈力球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 反正也不是什座熱賣商品…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…於是就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 一個超級彈力球都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊 這店真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 現在斷貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還特意起了個早想中個大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得粗點心店重新開業 這不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麽看來馬上又要關門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去便利店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了 這麽下去這幾個小孩兒就不會再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想 好好思考下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 少年們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們難道不想要大號的彈力球…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要"自已想要的"尺寸的彈力球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹽和水還有洗衣液 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是指這個 彈力球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是猴急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可變不成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 在杯裝的冰里加入食鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後攪拌均勻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著加入洗衣漿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 那邊猴急的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡什麽顔色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才不猴急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這裡就選姐姐喜歐的孔雀藍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杯子裡加一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杷這個好好攪拌的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彈力球就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是球形的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是性急啊 這樣會不受女孩子歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個滴溜滴溜地搓圓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水份擠出來了就擦乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就擦在衣服上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓搓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這就是你專用的彈力球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…專用 專用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 姐姐你是煉金術師嗎
